[
    {
        "content": "<p>I just realized it'd be possible to use the \"record builder\" syntax <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"489294\">@Agus Zubiaga</span> recently implemented to implement a generator for sequential unique IDs - something like this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Python\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">bar</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">baz</span> <span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Count</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">foo</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;-</span> <span class=\"n\">Count</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inc</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"c1\"># increment by 1</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">bar</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;-</span> <span class=\"n\">Count</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inc</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">baz</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;-</span> <span class=\"n\">Count</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inc</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">Count</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">done</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 367276843,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1687051522
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I did <a href=\"https://package.elm-lang.org/packages/rtfeldman/count/latest/\">something similar in Elm</a> a long time ago</p>",
        "id": 367276957,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1687051587
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>basically this is a way to avoid doing like:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Python\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">foo</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"n\">bar</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"n\">baz</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>...and then having to manually keep them all sequential, check for duplicates, etc.</p>",
        "id": 367277070,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1687051653
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you could also replace <code>Count.inc</code> with a custom function which (for example) wraps the number in an opaque type like <code>MyId</code> or whatever</p>",
        "id": 367277261,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1687051764
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>or transforms it however you like</p>",
        "id": 367277269,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1687051772
    }
]